	dprr:hasNoteText "Brother and Quaestor (by 40, Proquaestor) of L. Decidius Saxa, who was resisting Labienus and the Parthians when deserted by his troops, who were former soldiers of Brutus and Cassius (Dio 48.25.2)." .
